title: Bobby Gets Shamed For Wearing A Jersey On His Date + Lauren Alaina on How Much Weight She Has Lost on DWTS + Bobby’s Mailbag: Boyfriend Keeps Saying He Will Propose
itunes:title: Bobby Gets Shamed For Wearing A Jersey On His Date + Lauren Alaina on How Much Weight She Has Lost on DWTS + Bobby’s Mailbag: Boyfriend Keeps Saying He Will Propose
description:
Bobby went on a date to a Titans game his weekend and wore a jersey. Lunchbox calls him out saying she probably thought he was lame for doing that. We talk to Lauren Alaina about how much weight she’s lost on Dancing with The Stars going into another week. Bobby reads an email from a listener who is struggling with her boyfriend who keeps saying he will propose.
